    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i have this really sharp pain in my lower right stomach area. it started around my belly button earlier today but now it's moved down and to the right. u think its just bad gas or maybe like period cramps? feeling kinda nauseous too. can i take some strong ibuprofen so i can just sleep it off?",
